chingowy, kt\u00f3ry oferuje przyst\u0119pne szkolenia i grupowe sesje. To doskona\u0142a okazja do nauki i wymiany do\u015bwiadcze\u0144 z innymi sprzedawcami.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, zarz\u0105dzanie kontem na Amazonie to z\u0142o\u017cony proces, ale z odpowiedni\u0105 wiedz\u0105 i wsparciem mo\u017cesz znacz\u0105co poprawi\u0107 swoje wyniki. Nie zapomnij korzysta\u0107 z dost\u0119pnych narz\u0119dzi i zasob\u00f3w, aby rozwija\u0107 sw\u00f3j biznes.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak efektywnie zarz\u0105dza\u0107 swoim kontem na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy jeste\u015b sprzedawc\u0105 na Amazonie i czu<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5770,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5769","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5769"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5769"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5769\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5770"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5769"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5769"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand